The block-based sorted-list design used by Goblin Core's zset implementation was
informed by Sorted Containers:

  Python Sorted Containers
  Copyright 2014-2024 Grant Jenks
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0
  https://github.com/grantjenks/python-sortedcontainers
  https://grantjenks.com/docs/sortedcontainers/implementation.html

Goblin Core does not vendor Sorted Containers source code. The C++ implementation
is an independent implementation of the documented design approach: sorted
blocks, per-block maximum values, and a compact rank index.

